Simple query script for stats.xonotic.org

Installation:
  * On Arch Linux, you may install from the AUR the 'xonstat' package;
    see https://aur.archlinux.org/packages/xonstat-git for details.
  * Otherwise, copy the xonstat script into a directory that is in your
    $PATH.

Usage:
  xonstat <player-id>

License:
  GNU GPL3

Example output:
  $ xonstat 9214
  Nick        | [Regulars] Isi Going
  Date joined | Fri 22 Jun 21:54:32 CEST 2012
  Last played | Sat 11 Apr 20:22:51 CEST 2015
  K/D ratio   | 1.99 (94557/47588)
  FCK         | 27276
  C/P ratio   | 0.45 (14119/31399)
  Highest ELO | 1494.54 (Î”1494.5371921215794)
         Mode | ctf
         Rank | 2 out of 631
   Percentile | 99.84
